{"tid":1470692,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"請保持初心及理智","createTime":"2019-08-14T06:18:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T06:35:47.000Z","uid":201837,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c4453e3966d041bfd7761609ecb8e4ac7b0f59a6","tid":1470692,"uid":201837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:18:25.000Z","msg":"緊記 不分化 不割蓆 不篤灰<br />\n諗番兩個月以黎喺點樣走過<br />\n請唔好放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n鬼係需要提防，但唔係無時無刻都諗點捉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只要你地知道自己做緊咩，唔好隨便畀人煽動，保持思考，鬼搞唔到你幾多。<br />\n反而真正嘅手足會因為咁擔心被人割庶<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有咩做錯咗，係要諗吓點兜，而唔係互相責罵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明白有時大家火氣重，但係屌完請你諗吓點補救會更好<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「核爆都唔割」係對手足嘅承諾<br />\n「兄弟爬山各自努力」係對唔同諗法嘅包容<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"76aed6b5689b2764806d2c2103016b6caa7082db","tid":1470692,"uid":201837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:35:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"30d0c3e4d6e8648b55457fa15da6ea67ea1d2005","tid":1470692,"uid":201837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:35:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6bd77dc8dcdad4bdde78c5b5d409ef39eff9f4a8","tid":1470692,"uid":201837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:35:47.000Z","msg":"推"}]}